{"tid":1628534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以幫我推俾前線手足睇","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:26:44.000Z","uid":158020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9845e94e60ea6c1302c76cfedaaf636b87af84","tid":1628534,"uid":158020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:26:13.000Z","msg":"前線手足 首先多謝你地辛苦咗咁多個月<br />\n鑑於而家你地身邊邊個係狗 真係好難分辨 引至裝修鶳究竟係邊個做無人知 當然大家都話呢個時勢已經唔使再理外人點睇 但係記住<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民主係一場鬥人多嘅遊戲 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n關於裝修 鶳我有少少意見<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑店-指曾令手足受傷 曾出賣港人</span></strong><br />\n（麻雀館 党鉄 美心全部業務 優品 係例子）我個人認為應該大裝 裝修時不妨留返幾隻大字話俾人知點解會有裝修工程 呢啲舖頭無實際嘅貨物 例如iphone ipad 唔會俾人趁火打劫 優品就係舖頭門口set rb <br />\n註： 党鉄必須大裝 手足死傷最嚴重<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅店-泛指支那生意 黎香港呃香港人錢</span></span></strong><br />\n呢啲係舖頭外面畫下畫寫下字<br />\n（近期常出現嘅係中移 中銀 小米 三中商）<br />\n個人認為出版有自由 賣咩書都有自由 所以粉飾門面就足夠<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍店-其實背後只係一班生意人 </span></strong>講到底都係為錢 我地罷食罷買就得<br />\n<br />\n<ins>鶳方面</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>只有口角者 </strong></span>可以唔理 展現我地有言論自由 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講粗口者即係擾亂公眾秩序</span></strong> 綁起幫佢紋個身 我以後唔講粗口<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">赤手空拳但係先郁手者</span></strong> 手足有權自衛 制伏後走人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">持有武器者</span></strong> 鶳唔該<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核爆都唔割<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a759919891ec5d0d0b9c74b99244c0bb48877273","tid":1628534,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=5ef54810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a>"}]}